## Platform & Operations

### Full German Translation

The entire Sellfaster interface is now available in German. Language is set per user account and all labels, error messages, and documentation pages are fully localised. We are launching with English and German; more languages are on the roadmap.

### Documentation

A full user guide is now live at [sellfaster.eu/docs](https://sellfaster.eu/docs), covering every feature in both English and German. Each section includes step-by-step instructions, tables, and annotated screenshots.

### Audit Log

Team owners can review a change history for key records — dashboards, interaction states, sale models — showing who made what change and when. This makes it straightforward to investigate unexpected configuration changes and maintain accountability across large teams.

### Performance Improvements

This release includes significant under-the-hood improvements to page load times, map rendering, and list pagination. Large datasets that previously felt sluggish should be noticeably faster.

